# Volatility compression precedes expansion. When BTC's daily range has
# contracted hard and price pushes through the upper band anyway, that is
# the squeeze firing — ride the expansion with a trailing stop instead of
# capping it with a fixed target.

strategy "BTC Squeeze Breakout"

when $BTC-USD at [upper_bollinger] and [quiet 2.5%]
  buy [$5000]

sell when [trailing 4%]
  or [after 20 bars]
